OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,FThe son of Ricky Hatton has opened up
OL,7,Fabout about losing his dad, as he
OL,8,Flaunches a foundation set up in the
OL,9,Fformer boxing champion's name.
OL,11,FThe 46-year-old was found dead at his
OL,12,Fat home in Hyde, Greater Manchester on
OL,13,FSunday 14, September.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV's Good Morning
OL,16,FBritain, Campbell Hatton said: "It's
OL,17,Fbeen a bit of a whirlwind the last few
OL,18,Fweeks, obviously we've been leading up
OL,19,Fto the funeral, which was unbelievable
OL,20,Fto see the amount of love everyone had
OL,21,Ffor my dad.
