OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,F"There were thousands in the streets
OL,7,Fand there's a lot of comfort to take
OL,8,Ffrom that.
OL,10,F"It has been very up and down really,
OL,11,Fbut as a family we're just trying to
OL,12,Ftake each day at a time."
OL,14,FA memorial for Ricky took place on
OL,15,FFriday 10 October, where thousands of
OL,16,Fpeople lined the streets to say an
OL,17,Femotional farewell to the World
OL,18,FChampion Boxer.
