OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,FCampbell said: "He always said that he
OL,7,Fwas more proud of his fanbase than he
OL,8,Fwas all the belts and the titles.
OL,10,F"It was obvious how much he was loved
OL,11,Fby the amount of people that followed
OL,12,Fhim all over the world to watch him
OL,13,Fbox, but to actually see everyone in
OL,14,Fthe streets, it was a very long route
OL,15,Fthat we went down and there was never
OL,16,Fa point where the streets weren't full.
OL,18,F"To actually see it in terms of the
OL,19,Famount of people, it was surreal
OL,20,Freally."
