OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,FThe first inquest hearing took place
OL,7,Fon Thursday 16 October, where a
OL,8,Fcoroner's court heard the former
OL,9,FBoxing World Champion was found dead
OL,10,Fafter taking his own life at his home.
OL,12,F"He was just himself all the time and
OL,13,FI think that's what people liked. He
OL,14,Fhad a good sense of humour, he could
OL,15,Fhave a laugh at himself, like normal
OL,16,Fpeople can."
OL,18,FCampbell revealed that over the last
OL,19,F12 months, he has been struggling with
OL,20,Fhis own mental health.
