OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,FHe shared that The Ricky Hatton
OL,7,FFoundation had been set up to help
OL,8,Fothers who may be suffering from
OL,9,Fmental health issues.
OL,11,FTalking about the foundation, he said:
OL,12,F"It's still very early days with
OL,13,Feverything but a big part of it is
OL,14,Fgoing to be around sport and educating
OL,15,Fpeople."
OL,17,FCampbell explained that a lot of
OL,18,Fsports "can be quite a lonely place,"
OL,19,Fso after retirement "you can feel a
OL,20,Fbit lost."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
