OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,FHe added: "It's looking to get in
OL,7,Fearly and educate people as soon as
OL,8,Fthey get involved in sport, and
OL,9,Fraising awareness in other ways.
OL,11,F"The foundation is something we've
OL,12,Fbeen looking to do for a while and
OL,13,Fwe've never had the right time. Now is
OL,14,Fas good as time as we can get to carry
OL,15,Fhis legacy on and start tackling
OL,16,Fmental health.
OL,18,F"The motto is 'no one should fight
OL,19,Falone' and it's going to be looking at
OL,20,Fhelping sportsmen, men, anyone really
OL,21,Fwho's struggling with mental health.
