OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,F"Educating, raising awareness, and
OL,7,Factively tackling it through money
OL,8,Fraised so people don't have to
OL,9,Fstruggle alone."
OL,11,FCampbell shared that the foundation
OL,12,Fwas an initiative that he had spoken
OL,13,Fabout with his father. He said: "We
OL,14,Fspoke about how little (mental health)
OL,15,Fis spoken about and how much stigma is
OL,16,Fstill around, especially with men
OL,17,Ftalking about your feelings.
