OL,3,C'No one should fight alone': Ricky
OL,4,CHatton's son speaks up about his dad
OL,6,F"It's wrongly not seen as a macho
OL,7,Fthing to do. People still can see a
OL,8,Fbit of weakness in it, but this is
OL,9,Flooking to try and change that.
OL,11,F"I think with my dad's name attached
OL,12,Fto it, I think a lot of that stigma
OL,13,Fand people seeing it as a weakness
OL,14,Fwill go because obviously as a
OL,15,Fprofessional world champion boxer, you
OL,16,Fdon't get much tougher than that, so
OL,17,Fif he can talk about his struggles, I
OL,18,Fthink anyone can."
